OL,4,Can education centre in the Borders
OL,6,FA public consultation has been
OL,7,Flaunched on a proposal to permanently
OL,8,Fclose The Wilton Centre in Hawick.
OL,10,FThe centre, also know as The Arches,
OL,11,Fhas been temporarily closed since the
OL,12,Fpandemic.
