OL,3,CConsultation into permanent closure of
OL,4,Can education centre in the Borders
OL,6,FScottish Border Council say support is
OL,7,Fnow provided in mainstream schools,
OL,8,Finstead of the standalone Wilton
OL,9,Fbuilding, which has "reduced travel
OL,10,Ftime for children, and created a more
OL,11,Finclusive service within the
OL,12,Fchildren's own communities".
OL,14,FLocal authorities say the building
OL,15,Fwould need "significant investment" to
OL,16,Fbe able to provide services.
